{
  "stem": "19921.4",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 80.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we had two shells, special shells for destruction.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And, thank God, we didn't have to use it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There were a couple of times that we came pretty close because we were surrounded and a couple of times we had to leave in a hurry.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But thank God, we didn't have to use it, and I didn't use it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So that, those guns-- those shells were surrounded, surrendered after the war.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was my responsibility.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had 88 people, a self, self-sufficient unit with our own kitchen and everything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Of course, we didn't have any homes to live in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we had that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, thank God, with this unit, with this unit actually I went through the whole war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were starting, starting in the Smolensk area, occupying, you know, the, the west, the east, eastern, not the-- well, the west part of Poland, like cities Lublin, Chelm, Wlodawa, and Warsaw, and going all the way down from that area to [NON-ENGLISH] and so forth, the port city of Szczecin, and all the way down to Berlin.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And finally, we terminated our stint in Berlin with this particular gun.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, absolutely.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were great fighting in Russia and smaller advancements, not bigger advancement.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The advancement came mostly in spring because that was wintertime.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in wintertime, you couldn't do too much because there was just too much snow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In wintertime, we had to stay 24 hours guard and just shoveling the snow down with wooden shovels because there's a tremendous amount of snow in that particular time, you know, in 1943, '44.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Spring '44.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Absolutely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Spring, '44.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And finally, we came to the, to the borders.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We actually came to the Polish borders in July of 1944.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In July of 1944.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "July of 1944.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
